definitions.definition: Something added to food to sweeten its taste , especially an artificial substitute for sugar .
Something given or added to added to a deal to sweeten another 's attitude , especially a bribe or kickback .
A shill bidder at an auction .

main_definition: Something added to food to sweeten its taste , especially an artificial substitute for sugar .
